::Ramulus::

Ramulus frowns. He wasn't sure if there was a blank protoform aboard the 
Cybertronian Fire, but they could still check.

He nods. "Ok, we can check in the storage. Follow me," he says, turing to 
walk toward the Cybertronian Fire. He was a bit confused by all this, but if 
this was a Maximal, he had to help it.
